description: This file declares APIs for managing Vendor Log Files in the COSA Data Model, including functions to get, set, validate, commit, and rollback configuration parameters related to vendor logs.

methods.name: VendorLogFile_GetEntryCount
methods.description: Retrieves the number of Vendor Log File entries.

methods.name: VendorLogFile_GetEntry
methods.description: Gets a specific Vendor Log File entry based on index.

methods.name: VendorLogFile_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Gets a boolean parameter value for a vendor log file entry.

methods.name: VendorLogFile_GetParamIntValue
methods.description: Gets an integer parameter value for a vendor log file entry.

methods.name: VendorLogFile_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Gets a ULONG parameter value for a vendor log file entry.

methods.name: VendorLogFile_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Gets a string parameter value for a vendor log file entry.

methods.name: VendorLogFile_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets a boolean parameter value for a vendor log file entry.

methods.name: VendorLogFile_SetParamIntValue
methods.description: Sets an integer parameter value for a vendor log file entry.

methods.name: VendorLogFile_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Sets a ULONG parameter value for a vendor log file entry.

methods.name: VendorLogFile_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets a string parameter value for a vendor log file entry.

methods.name: VendorLogFile_Validate
methods.description: Validates the parameters of a vendor log file entry before applying changes.

methods.name: VendorLogFile_Commit
methods.description: Commits changes to a vendor log file entry.

methods.name: VendorLogFile_Rollback
methods.description: Rolls back changes to a vendor log file entry.
